    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a dependable daily driver. While the car is mechanically sound and drives well, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows signs of heavy use, and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to reach full cooling capacity. It has been regularly maintained, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few months. This is an honest, high-mileage car that still has plenty of life left for a practical buyer.",
