    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to be listing this absolute beauty. It has been pampered since day one and is in truly flawless condition\u2014it basically still has that new car smell! You really have to see it in person to appreciate how pristine it is; it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this perfect ride. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
