      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman S, maintained to a concourse standard. This mid-engine masterpiece features the 2.5L turbocharged flat-four equipped with Variable Turbine Geometry (VTG), delivering a linear torque curve and 350hp. The chassis is enhanced with PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) and PTV (Porsche Torque Vectoring) featuring a mechanical rear differential lock for surgical turn-in. Mated to a lightning-fast 7-speed PDK transmission, the drivetrain remains factory-spec and unmodified. The exterior paint retains its deep luster with zero rock chips, while the cabin shows no bolster wear or UV degradation. Full service documentation confirms proactive maintenance of all critical seals, fluids, and the cooling system. This is a turn-key, high-performance machine for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
